args: What's this bug cage doing here?
Don't give me that! Was it you?! Were you\nthe one that threw bugs into my room?
Why would I do something like that?
What are you staring at...? Oh! The cage?
Look, it was just sitting here. I don't know\nwhere it came from, I swear.
I know it sounds like I'm making up\nexcuses, but it... I... Um...
...No. Now that I think about it, you really\nhave no reason to act in such a manner.
Why? It isn't as if you have anything to\napologize for. ...Riiight?
True, but I...just felt like I should say it.
*sigh* You are a strange one. Sometimes\nyour kindness gets the better of you.
Is that so? Um, ha ha...
Huh? I think someone's calling me.
Why is there a laundry bucket here?\nTsk! The floor's all wet. I better hurry\nand mop this up...
Owww... For Ilia's sake, why is the floor\ncovered in suds?!
Sorry! But it wasn't me! Or...\nWell, I guess it was, actually.
I know that you are not the kind of person\nto do this as some sort of prank...
But still, I would appreciate a bit more\nconsideration! People could slip and hurt\nthemselves, you know.
Thanks for helping me organize this room,\nEstelle.
You are most welcome. I must say, though,\nit's rather odd for royalty to engage in\ntasks like this.
Whether a person is royalty or not doesn't\nmatter much around here. Now then, it\nshould be riiight baaack...
This room is certainly...＂cozy.＂ And dusty.\nAnd full of all sorts of strange things.
Gah! What happened to the lights?!
Estelle! Estelle, are you okay?! Aahhh!
Owww... S-sorry, Estelle...\nSomething caught my leg...
I-it's fine... But could...could you just\nmove, maybe?
I should be the one saying that!
Honestly, will your tomfoolery never end?!
I-I'm sorry! But I don't mean to—
Not you. ...You might as well come out!\nI know you're there!
What?! When did this kid get in here?!
You realize you've been the target of all\nthose pranks, right? Well, you're looking\nat the culprit.
Hey! You just ratted me out!
Of course, I would never allow you to get\naway with such behavior! You've earned\nyourself a Loving Hand!
Again? You know that doesn't\neven hurt!
Then as FURTHER punishment, you are\ngoing to clean the church from tip to toe!
For Ilia's sake, I hope this will teach him\na lesson.
Hey, Estelle? Could you do that to me,\ntoo?
What? But those pranks weren't your\nfault...
Still, I made you upset, didn't I?
I think I'd feel like I made it up to you that\nway.
Thanks. Now I feel less guilty.
The Loving Hand is supposed to make\npeople reflect on their actions, and yet\nyou feel absolved...
Heh. Well, this is a special case.
It's only your Loving Hand that could make\nme feel like that.
